      • sendScreenFade

        public void sendScreenFade(java.lang.String text,
                           int state,
                           int seconds)
        Sends some information to the client about screen fading.
        Parameters:
        text - the text that will be displayed in the center of the screen
        state - the state should be either 0, -1, or 1.
        seconds - the amount of time in seconds it takes for the fade to transition.

        If the state is -1 then the screen fades from black to transparent. When the state is +1 the screen fades from transparent to black. If the state is 0 all drawing is stopped.
